legs.end_address: Πάροδος Γ. Δροσίνη 1Α, Ασβεστοχώρι, 57010, Pefka 570 10, Greece

steps.html_instructions:
Take the Skiathos - Volos ferry to Βόλος
Toll road
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto Grigoriou Lampraki
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit and stay on Grigoriou Lampraki
At the roundabout, continue straight onto Larisis/EO6

Keep right at the fork, follow signs for LARISSA/A1 and merge onto A/D Pireos Athinon Thessalonikis Evzonon/A1/E75
Toll road

Keep right to continue on Egnatia Odos/A1/A2/E90
Toll road
At the interchange 21, keep right and follow signs for A2/E90 toward KAVALA-SERRES/CHALKIDIKI

Turn right onto Drosini
Destination will be on the left
